Instructions to run the project :-
1. first, clone project.
2. open terminal for same folder and run command :- npm i
3. then run the command :- npm start
4. then go to  your browser and search -
http://localhost:5000/
project will run

or 
you can direct access project by this link project is hosted on this link
https://chat-room-3mbg.onrender.com/

then create a room with unique roomName and userName and start chating multiple users can chat in same room .
multiple room can be created be created at a time.

we made a static web chat room where peaple can create room and chat.
most of the part is backend MERNstack specific
we used Node.js with express,javascript and mongodb databse as data storage.
for fronend we used ejs template engine.
